title: Avengers: Endgame
plot: After the devastating events of Avengers: Infinity War (2018), the universe is in ruins due to the efforts of the Mad Titan, Thanos. With the help of remaining allies, the Avengers must assemble once more in order to undo Thanos's actions and undo the chaos to the universe, no matter what consequences may be in store, and no matter who they face...
awards: Top Rated Movies #76 | Nominated for 1 Oscar. Another 69 wins & 111 nominations.
writers: Christopher Markus, Stephen McFeely, Stan Lee, Jack Kirby, Joe Simon, Steve Englehart, Steve Gan, Bill Mantlo, Keith Giffen, Jim Starlin, Larry Lieber, Don Heck
stars: Robert Downey Jr., Chris Evans, Mark Ruffalo, Chris Hemsworth

similars.title: Avengers: Infinity War
similars.plot: The Avengers and their allies must be willing to sacrifice all in an attempt to defeat the powerful Thanos before his blitz of devastation and ruin puts an end to the universe.
similars.stars: Robert Downey Jr., Chris Hemsworth, Mark Ruffalo

similars.title: Thor: Ragnarok
similars.plot: Imprisoned on the planet Sakaar, Thor must race against time to return to Asgard and stop Ragnark, the destruction of his world, at the hands of the powerful and ruthless villain Hela.
similars.stars: Chris Hemsworth, Tom Hiddleston, Cate Blanchett

similars.title: The Avengers
similars.plot: Earth's mightiest heroes must come together and learn to fight as a team if they are going to stop the mischievous Loki and his alien army from enslaving humanity.
similars.stars: Robert Downey Jr., Chris Evans, Scarlett Johansson

similars.title: Avengers: Age of Ultron
similars.plot: When Tony Stark and Bruce Banner try to jump-start a dormant peacekeeping program called Ultron, things go horribly wrong and it's up to Earth's mightiest heroes to stop the villainous Ultron from enacting his terrible plan.
similars.stars: Robert Downey Jr., Chris Evans, Mark Ruffalo

similars.title: Captain America: Civil War
similars.plot: Political involvement in the Avengers' affairs causes a rift between Captain America and Iron Man.
similars.stars: Chris Evans, Robert Downey Jr., Scarlett Johansson

similars.title: Joker
similars.plot: In Gotham City, mentally troubled comedian Arthur Fleck is disregarded and mistreated by society. He then embarks on a downward spiral of revolution and bloody crime. This path brings him face-to-face with his alter-ego: the Joker.
similars.stars: Joaquin Phoenix, Robert De Niro, Zazie Beetz

similars.title: The Dark Knight
similars.plot: When the menace known as the Joker wreaks havoc and chaos on the people of Gotham, Batman must accept one of the greatest psychological and physical tests of his ability to fight injustice.
similars.stars: Christian Bale, Heath Ledger, Aaron Eckhart

similars.title: Black Panther
similars.plot: T'Challa, heir to the hidden but advanced kingdom of Wakanda, must step forward to lead his people into a new future and must confront a challenger from his country's past.
similars.stars: Chadwick Boseman, Michael B. Jordan, Lupita Nyong'o

similars.title: Inception
similars.plot: A thief who steals corporate secrets through the use of dream-sharing technology is given the inverse task of planting an idea into the mind of a C.E.O.
similars.stars: Leonardo DiCaprio, Joseph Gordon-Levitt, Elliot Page

similars.title: The Dark Knight Rises
similars.plot: Eight years after the Joker's reign of anarchy, Batman, with the help of the enigmatic Catwoman, is forced from his exile to save Gotham City from the brutal guerrilla terrorist Bane.
similars.stars: Christian Bale, Tom Hardy, Anne Hathaway

similars.title: Captain America: The Winter Soldier
similars.plot: As Steve Rogers struggles to embrace his role in the modern world, he teams up with a fellow Avenger and S.H.I.E.L.D agent, Black Widow, to battle a new threat from history: an assassin known as the Winter Soldier.
similars.stars: Chris Evans, Samuel L. Jackson, Scarlett Johansson

similars.title: Guardians of the Galaxy
similars.plot: A group of intergalactic criminals must pull together to stop a fanatical warrior with plans to purge the universe.
similars.stars: Chris Pratt, Vin Diesel, Bradley Cooper
